files.content:
"use client"

import React from "react"

export const Check = React.forwardRef<
  SVGSVGElement,
  React.SVGAttributes<SVGSVGElement>
>(function (props, ref) {
  return (
    <svg
      ref={ref}
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="1em"
      height="1em"
      viewBox="0 0 52 52"
      stroke="currentColor"
      {...props}
    >
      <path
        fill="none"
        strokeWidth="8"
        strokeLinecap="round"
        strokeLinejoin="round"
        d="M10 27l10 12 25-25"
        strokeDasharray="50"
        strokeDashoffset="50"
      >
        <animate
          attributeName="stroke-dashoffset"
          values="50;0"
          dur="0.1s"
          fill="freeze"
        />
      </path>
    </svg>
  )
})

Check.displayName = "Check"
